loading="lazy"
alt="Dark Crystal in Patchbay"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="121"
data-flex-basis="291px"
&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We presented our work at &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pOloj658DtQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;DevCon 4&lt;/a&gt;
and this led to grants from the Ethereum Foundation, further iterations on
protocol, user-research, partnership with Briar, a java implementation and more.&lt;/p&gt;
